{"tid":2489714,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"日本書係咪多數亂鳩咁黎","createTime":"2021-04-15T06:14:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T06:55:47.000Z","uid":93141,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0651a8151f9b44b1f2148d545f5a2ce1edf618bf","tid":2489714,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:14:30.000Z","msg":"屌那星近排睇歷史書，近代史多<br />\n日本作者既歷史書全部都垃撚圾，應該唔係單純譯者問題<br />\n<br />\n你老味好似睇緊連登仔講野咁<br />\n一係九唔搭八唔通順，呢樣都可以話係譯者問題<br />\n一係就空泛冇內容，標題吸引但內容膚淺<br />\n一係漂住一陣右翼味，成日想坐時光機贏二戰<br />\n仲要日本本位以為自己好撚重要，讀者熟知日本堆細微濕鳩野先可以睇<br />\n而家一睇書名似內容農場就知本書係日本作者<br />\n唔單止係歷史書，科學同哲學好多都係咁，係文學有得照作者原意好返少少<br />\n<br />\n歐美/台灣既歷史書普遍就正常返好多，行文流暢唔多講，識得抽離用第三身角度講，就算面對屠殺/奴隸制/共產堆野都係有critical thinking，分析前因後果，唔會下下左膠/右膠咁批評/支持，source有可信性<br />\n<br />\n諗起就扯火，電子書冇得preview好多，台仔又咁撚鍾意入日本書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：買中譯本目的係想睇閒書，正經學時都係睇返原文<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c720398e531e847a9c0ee97737825a04f19340d","tid":2489714,"uid":373438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:16:52.000Z","msg":"所以咪養肥左嗰隻老高囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ad2797116daf4a6d2a1bdb85cbffb218fa15db","tid":2489714,"uid":93141,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c720398e531e847a9c0ee97737825a04f19340d","tid":2489714,"uid":373438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:16:52.000Z","msg":"所以咪養肥左嗰隻老高囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:18:40.000Z","msg":"唉屌，真係同老高講野差唔多<br />\n而家買完冇得退，del都del唔到，擺響到阻頭阻勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ae0bbb0c0a716fbe0ae58278e7bcfee768715e","tid":2489714,"uid":36673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:23:14.000Z","msg":"日本出版量好商，各種奇奇怪怪嘅書都有<br />\n寫下blog又出書，又翻譯到做中文出版<br />\n睇台譯歷史書一定要揀下出版社<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ac8db91b6fd94802b31401c2f2406a76e706308","tid":2489714,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:24:00.000Z","msg":"流通既多數好鳩<br />\n寫得好既得一兩版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb6ec5ca16b2e3772527e37417d80b37569635f1","tid":2489714,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b0ae0bbb0c0a716fbe0ae58278e7bcfee768715e","tid":2489714,"uid":36673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:23:14.000Z","msg":"日本出版量好商，各種奇奇怪怪嘅書都有<br />\n寫下blog又出書，又翻譯到做中文出版<br />\n睇台譯歷史書一定要揀下出版社<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:31:27.000Z","msg":"日譯中堆選擇真係好撚奇怪<br />\n歐美譯中既多數都係暢銷書，日本就好似咩twitter熱門都譯一餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.books.com.tw/products/E050055010\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.books.com.tw%2Fproducts%2FE050055010&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sDe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=aa7b8f01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.books.com.tw/products/E050055010</a><br />\n見佢咁推，入面揀左幾本同歐洲/東南亞有關既，全部都係垃圾，好彩冇貪平買全套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350512a25d0f661e32be98960c19a4e16b1a30d2","tid":2489714,"uid":166350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:31:49.000Z","msg":"睇歷史書都係要睇返鬼佬嘢<br />\n<br />\n利申：歷史系"},{"pid":"f96a34ed2b07e46167cbe3c38f70fa48982bc9aa","tid":2489714,"uid":93141,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"350512a25d0f661e32be98960c19a4e16b1a30d2","tid":2489714,"uid":166350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:31:49.000Z","msg":"睇歷史書都係要睇返鬼佬嘢<br />\n<br />\n利申：歷史系"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:35:44.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪門檻問題，歐美書多數都係prof出返，正氣好多<br />\n東亞/東南亞史睇台仔都ok既，中日韓既書真係唔想掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ad753a4d9e68a551b033b27f017beced112d44f","tid":2489714,"uid":218716,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:38:15.000Z","msg":"可能係市場規模問題<br />\n日本書得日台港市場<br />\n歐美書全球市場<br />\n香港書得港台市場<br />\n<br />\n冇錢就hea 寫，係咁現實。<br />\n<br />\n不過大前研一的日本低IQ 問題可能對，因為全世界都有呢個情況，但佢D 書都係差過歐美的。"},{"pid":"6f8db5ada14cfe3a9fd53074faf11e618cfbad08","tid":2489714,"uid":218716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cb6ec5ca16b2e3772527e37417d80b37569635f1","tid":2489714,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b0ae0bbb0c0a716fbe0ae58278e7bcfee768715e","tid":2489714,"uid":36673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:23:14.000Z","msg":"日本出版量好商，各種奇奇怪怪嘅書都有<br />\n寫下blog又出書，又翻譯到做中文出版<br />\n睇台譯歷史書一定要揀下出版社<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:31:27.000Z","msg":"日譯中堆選擇真係好撚奇怪<br />\n歐美譯中既多數都係暢銷書，日本就好似咩twitter熱門都譯一餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.books.com.tw/products/E050055010\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.books.com.tw%2Fproducts%2FE050055010&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sDe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=aa7b8f01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.books.com.tw/products/E050055010</a><br />\n見佢咁推，入面揀左幾本同歐洲/東南亞有關既，全部都係垃圾，好彩冇貪平買全套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:39:07.000Z","msg":"呢本都係日本professor 出的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69cee9dbd6a33c34103bab5dcf5e28ac3111dafd","tid":2489714,"uid":107186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:41:03.000Z","msg":"買左本《世界史是打出來的》，睇左幾章就頂唔順"},{"pid":"de26727604c7de0382579261e41f9090c66ab88c","tid":24897