e768715e","tid":2489714,"uid":36673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:23:14.000Z","msg":"日本出版量好商，各種奇奇怪怪嘅書都有<br />\n寫下blog又出書，又翻譯到做中文出版<br />\n睇台譯歷史書一定要揀下出版社<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:31:27.000Z","msg":"日譯中堆選擇真係好撚奇怪<br />\n歐美譯中既多數都係暢銷書，日本就好似咩twitter熱門都譯一餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.books.com.tw/products/E050055010\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.books.com.tw%2Fproducts%2FE050055010&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sDe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=aa7b8f01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.books.com.tw/products/E050055010</a><br />\n見佢咁推，入面揀左幾本同歐洲/東南亞有關既，全部都係垃圾，好彩冇貪平買全套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:43:28.000Z","msg":"八旗啲書係意識形態行先多啲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e238a366894546a6ce3d7d5bce8afe9a4f99f5af","tid":2489714,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:44:07.000Z","msg":"係咪八旗嗰堆書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有輯書係譯談講社套世界史<br />\n先唔講有啲位翻譯得唔順<br />\n入邊真係有錯漏(但好少)，同有時會用「據說」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得呢啲係學術上都係唔可以接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且敘事重心好多都偏向唔太重要嘅細微野，反而成個歷史大發展寫得好麻麻，一啲學界仲有爭議嘅議題寫到好似定案咁，啲source又質量比較低<br />\n<br />\n睇過幾套NHK嘅歷史紀錄片，又係好鍾意講啲細微野，例如戰國武將嗰啲八卦野，但就唔會好有系統咁介紹嗰段時間嘅歷史主要發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講真<br />\n係認真學歷史嘅話，就最好要謹慎揀書<br />\n作者最好就係英美名牌大學做過教授<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw我見英美有唔少賣得嘅書嘅作者都係記者都會轉行做作家，我唔識評價，等睇過嘅人出黎講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14466d704e53474cc0b0bccfed95e22ae68732cc","tid":2489714,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"69cee9dbd6a33c34103bab5dcf5e28ac3111dafd","tid":2489714,"uid":107186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:41:03.000Z","msg":"買左本《世界史是打出來的》，睇左幾章就頂唔順"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:44:29.000Z","msg":"好在呢本我preview就覺得唔對路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有本《倒著看的世界史》，覺得個idea幾好，但實際寫法完全係倒果為因，去脈絡化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa389d039f710c1188140e80b4c50bd62abf86f","tid":2489714,"uid":105798,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:45:15.000Z","msg":"有冇例子"},{"pid":"87413a142b51158551ed8a49e10c6aeb4e044c62","tid":2489714,"uid":234945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"350512a25d0f661e32be98960c19a4e16b1a30d2","tid":2489714,"uid":166350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:31:49.000Z","msg":"睇歷史書都係要睇返鬼佬嘢<br />\n<br />\n利申：歷史系"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:45:25.000Z","msg":"點解嘅？鬼佬思維唔同啲？"},{"pid":"6eaf06160cd353943f388509bccaf61fe923743a","tid":2489714,"uid":3441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:46:04.000Z","msg":"日本人似乎鍾意睇書<br />\n所以好撚多奇奇怪怪嘅書<br />\n<br />\n利伸：有兩本日文數學書"},{"pid":"d1581433e0d970f5da7bcfee39ed8e1d47138819","tid":2489714,"uid":166350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f96a34ed2b07e46167cbe3c38f70fa48982bc9aa","tid":2489714,"uid":93141,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"350512a25d0f661e32be98960c19a4e16b1a30d2","tid":2489714,"uid":166350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:31:49.000Z","msg":"睇歷史書都係要睇返鬼佬嘢<br />\n<br />\n利申：歷史系"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:35:44.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪門檻問題，歐美書多數都係prof出返，正氣好多<br />\n東亞/東南亞史睇台仔都ok既，中日韓既書真係唔想掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:46:52.000Z","msg":"係，因為歐美嗰啲大部分真係學術研究嚟<br />\n如果你讀歷史係想當故仔咁聽嘅話，歐美啲書相對嚟講會好難入口，好悶（包括我自己）<br />\n日本仔嗰啲就唔評論，因為無睇過，而台仔出嗰啲算係歷史普及書，算係俾你認識下歷史咁"},{"pid":"fe76c00f3f88d2a8d573a0e427a1e9bad76326ae","tid":2489714,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:47:25.000Z","msg":"搵日本歷史書都係睇內亞、東北亞史觀"},{"pid":"d8141b9dc23464a560f00b8b535d162043d6088e","tid":2489714,"uid":75372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:47:33.000Z","msg":"有無例子?"},{"pid":"7c8a3c0ff46dfbbb9ad20da48a87577320100681","tid":2489714,"uid":93141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3ad753a4d9e68a551b033b27f017beced112d44f","tid":2489714,"uid":218716,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:38:15.000Z","msg":"可能係市場規模問題<br />\n日本書得日台港市場<br />\n歐美書全球市場<br />\n香港書得港台市場<br />\n<br />\n冇錢就hea 寫，係咁現實。<br />\n<br />\n不過大前研一的日本低IQ 問題可能對，因為全世界都有呢個情況，但佢D 書都係差過歐美的。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:47:56.000Z","msg":"應該同IQ冇關，而係佢地思想可能比較狹窄<br />\n情況有d似美國出品紀錄片，多數都係america-centric同埋內容農場，但呢個情況美國既書反而就冇咁嚴重咁解"},{"pid":"8047e3a3efb577240b0878171af254b429dbc34c","tid":2489714,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:48:04.000Z","msg":"日本史淨係信鬼佬寫既<img src=\"http://lifestyle.etnet.com.hk/diva/images/stories/167/2014/10/1010200japan.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flifestyle.etnet.com.hk%2Fdiva%2Fimages%2Fstories%2F167%2F2014%2F10%2F1010200japan.jpg&h=82c723af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca7486eae105cb2b07d89ab9470dfe0a344efe0b","tid":2489714,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2643f3f722fa615050ccb3afc293443a616123d","tid":2489714,"uid":61853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb6ec5ca16b2e3772527e37417d80b37569635f1","tid":2489714,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b0ae0bbb0c0a716fbe0ae58278e7bcfee768715e","tid":2489714,"uid":36673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2